        <h1>Preston "Monty" Montgomery Jones III Archive</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          After an experimental youth treatment rewrote more memories than wrinkles,
          Monty commissioned this archive so he could remember who he has been. Explore his life
          through curated cards and filter them to find just the story you need.
        </p>
        <div class="filters" role="group" aria-label="Filter timeline cards">
          <button class="filter-button active" data-filter="all">All</button>
          <button class="filter-button" data-filter="vitals">Vitals</button>
